Hiya Bruce. I did get a chance to play several of your files but I was late for work so never got a chance to reply and got home and took a long nap and forgot about group stuff for a while =)
   
  I worked almost 12 hours today and have group later tonight but I will try and check out some more of your files tomorrow.
   
  Great stuff from all of you. I know I dont say it enough or post enough feedback but I try and listen to everything as I read posts, I just dont always have time to reply to everyone. Thats why many of you know I am quicker to reply to private mail directed specifically at me rather than groups. When I do have time I share my thoughts. 
   
  Misty
